OL,3,CArrests after Kinder Surprise found to
OL,4,Ccontain cocaine
OL,6,FTwo people have been arrested after
OL,7,Fbags of what is believed to be cocaine
OL,8,Fwere found inside of a Kinder Surprise
OL,9,Fcapsule.
OL,11,FPolice were called to Lord Street in
OL,12,FSouthport after they received reports
OL,13,Fof a suspected drug deal outside of a
OL,14,Fhotel.
OL,16,FUpon approaching a man and a woman who
OL,17,Fwere "acting suspiciously" the woman
OL,18,Fran inside the hotel where she was
OL,19,Fdetained by officers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
