PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776777070
OL,3,CArrests after Kinder Surprise found to
OL,4,Ccontain cocaine
OL,6,FPolice went on to discover "a large
OL,7,Fquantity" of white powder believed to
OL,8,Fbe cocaine inside of a hotel room,
OL,9,Fwith some inside of a yellow plastic
OL,10,FKinder Surprise container.
OL,12,FA 52-year-old man and a 49-year-old
OL,13,Fwoman from Southport were arrested on
OL,14,Fsuspicion of possession with intent to
OL,15,Fsupply Class A drugs, suspected
OL,16,Fcocaine. They have been released under
OL,17,Finvestigation pending further
OL,18,Fenquiries.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
