OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776777070
OL,3,CArrests after Kinder Surprise found to
OL,4,Ccontain cocaine
OL,6,FSefton's Area Commander, Karl Baldwin
OL,7,Fsaid: "Officers from the Southport
OL,8,FNeighbourhood Team and the Southport
OL,9,FTown Centre Team, acting on community
OL,10,Finformation, launched a proactive
OL,11,Foperation to tackle this issue head on.
OL,13,F"Despite these initial arrests, we
OL,14,Fknow there is more to do. The
OL,15,Foperation will continue, targeting all
OL,16,Fcriminality but focussing on those
OL,17,Finvolved in serious and organised
OL,18,Fcrime.
OL,26,@oD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
