CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1776777070
OL,3,CArrests after Kinder Surprise found to
OL,4,Ccontain cocaine
OL,6,F"Serious organised crime gangs are
OL,7,Fclosely linked to serious violence,
OL,8,Foften using weapons such as firearms
OL,9,For knives, which is why it's so
OL,10,Fimportant we tackle it relentlessly.
OL,12,F"Stop searches, warrants, land
OL,13,Fsearches and arrests take place all
OL,14,Fyear round, and in many instances, it
OL,15,Fis thanks to the public who tell us
OL,16,Fwhere there are issues in the
OL,17,Fcommunity."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
